title: China Core Consumer Prices
description: Core Consumer Prices in China remained unchanged at 100.60 points in October from 100.60 points in September of 2022. Core Consumer Prices in China averaged 101.29 points from 2008 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 102.50 points in June of 2011 and a record low of 98.40 points in August of 2009. This page provides - China Core Consumer Prices - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Bureau of Statistics of China
